ss=\"tableLine\">&lt;&nbsp;80 cm</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Referens</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">94–102 cm</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">80–88 cm</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Ökad</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt;&nbsp;102 cm </div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">&gt;&nbsp;88 cm</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\">Mycket ökad</div></td></tr></tbody></table>",
